,25 Taos archeology]\n{{refend}}\n\n[[Category:Puebloan peoples| ]]\n[[Category:Oasisamerica cultures]]\n[[Category:Southwest tribes]]\n[[Category:Native American tribes in Arizona]]\n[[Category:Native American tribes in New Mexico]]\n[[Category:Native American tribes in Texas]]\n[[Category:Native American history of New Mexico]]\n", "name_user": "Nihiltres", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:Simplified hatnote syntax", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puebloans"}
