er]]\n|George Farr\n|1:45.57\n|-\n|2003\n|[[Seeking the Ring]] ([[Tie (draw)|DH]])\n|[[Slade Callaghan]]\n|[[Mark Frostad]]\n|[[Sam-Son Farm]]\n|1:44.23\n|-\n|2003\n|[[Brattothecore]] ([[Tie (draw)|DH]]) \n|[[Jake Barton (jockey)|Jake Barton]]\n|[[John A. Ross (horse trainer)|John A. Ross]]\n|Jam Jar Racing\n|1:44.23\n|-\n|2002\n|[[Silver Nithi]]\n|[[Mickey Walls]]\n|[[David R. Bell]]\n|Dick & Jo Ellen Shaw\n|1:44.00\n|-\n|2001\n|[[Quick Blue]]\n|[[Emile Ramsammy]] \n|[[Linda L. Rice]]\n|J. P. Lacombe \n|1:43.60\n|-\n|2000\n|[[Catch The Ring]]\n|[[Robert C. Landry|Robert Landry]]\n|[[Mark Frostad]]\n|[[Sam-Son Farm]]\n|1:45.64\n|-\n|1999\n|[[Synchronized (horse)|Synchronized]]\n|[[Tyrone Harding]]\n|[[Reade Baker]]\n|[[John A. Franks]]\n|1:44.67\n|-\n|1998\n|[[Regal Angela]]\n|[[Martin Ramirez (jockey)|Martin Ramirez]]\n|[[Robert P. Tiller]]\n|Hillsbrook Farms\n|1:46.80\n|-\n|1997\n|[[Nithi]]\n|[[Mickey Walls]]\n|[[David R. Bell]]\n|J. E. & R. F. Shaw\n|1:45.20\n|-\n|1996\n|[[Silent Fleet]]\n|[[Steve Bahen]]\n|[[Bernard Girault]]\n|Peter Chiodo\n|1:44.20\n|-\n|1995\n|[[Woolloomooloo (horse)|Woolloomooloo]] \n|[[Todd Kabel]]\n|[[David R. Bell]]\n|R. F. & J. E. Shaw\n|1:43.20\n|-\n|1994\n|[[Mysteriously]]\n|[[Todd Kabel]]\n|[[Daniel J. Vella]]\n|[[Frank Stronach]]\n|1:46.20\n|-\n|1993\n|[[Hey Hazel]]\n|[[Don Seymour]]\n|[[Roger Attfield]]\n|M. Canino\n|1:43.80\n|-\n|1992\n|[[Hope For A Breeze]]\n|[[Herb McCauley]]\n|[[Paul Nielsen]]\n|Hopefield Farm\n|1:43.80\n|-\n|1991\n|[[Wilderness Song]]\n|[[Francine Villeneuve]]\n|[[James E. Day]]\n|[[Sam-Son Farm]]\n|1:42.40\n|-\n|1990\n|[[Lubicon (horse)|Lubicon]]\n|[[Don Seymour]]\n|[[Roger Attfield]]\n|[[Kinghaven Farms]]\n|1:46.40\n|-\n|1989\n|[[Coral Bracelet]]\n|[[Sandy Hawley]]\n|[[Macdonald Benson]]\n|[[Windfields Farm]]\n|1:43.80\n|-\n|1988\n|[[Volterra (horse)|Volterra]]\n|[[Sandy Hawley]]\n|[[Patrick Collins (horseman)|Patrick Collins]]\n|[[Knob Hill Stable]]\n|1:45.00\n|-\n|1987\n|[[Ruling Angel]]\n|[[Dave Penna]]\n|